title: Molly-Mae: Behind it All
overview: A raw and intimate docu-series following Britain's biggest influencer, Molly-Mae Hague. With unprecedented access to Molly and her family in the months after the break-up that shook the world, we follow her as she launches her clothing brand and navigates life as a single Mum. Strong, vulnerable and driven, the series reveals a different side to Molly-Mae.
